{"tid":2274751,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"江嘉敏17歲細妹曝光 寸嘴直逼家姐","createTime":"2020-11-06T15:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T16:16:35.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4198fc386d6b08178313267f0f17f9246b1d04","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"是非多多的江嘉敏既寸嘴又鍾意撩事鬥飛，早前同馮盈盈隔空開火反面決裂，冇咗馮盈盈呢個好姊妹唔緊要，江嘉敏仲有兩個親生妹妹。日前江嘉敏生日，在IG限時動態tag了只有17歲的細妹帳號，令細妹意外曝光，有網友大讚佢同江<br />\n嘉敏似餅印，不過最似都係把寸嘴，同埋覺得自己好索成日玩自拍，姊妹果然同根生。"},{"pid":"2eb4b291524c7d4ad1a7f2867dce5e44973c2fbb","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo_2020-11-06_17-57-37_18950569505fa5251ed94e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fphoto_2020-11-06_17-57-37_18950569505fa5251ed94e3.jpg&h=8f6bd2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日前江嘉敏26歲生日，在IG的限時動態放了一張阿妹視角照，唔覺意令細妹的帳號曝光。"},{"pid":"c5e2dd7804061d1529686f3b863be846a189e51d","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cheuky1_93621206_150356706483694_8848699768860757646_n_15458939445fa5250b5e2f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fcheuky1_93621206_150356706483694_8848699768860757646_n_15458939445fa5250b5e2f9.jpg&h=b16f3f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細妹亦似江嘉敏咁貪靚，超級鍾意影女神相。"},{"pid":"62bce4a17304f50666b730ca5a49eeaceaaa16ab","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cheuky1_121600749_1825227424291759_7430740402057872292_n_8381514495fa52513c61da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fcheuky1_121600749_1825227424291759_7430740402057872292_n_8381514495fa52513c61da.jpg&h=8f64cf5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n17歲的細妹清純樣被指與江嘉敏好似樣。"},{"pid":"8338f577aa94bdbe763bb8fc63b66e3b5778797c","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cheuky1_106273080_313206323405717_2720353903420328948_n_12009864885fa5251064609.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fcheuky1_106273080_313206323405717_2720353903420328948_n_12009864885fa5251064609.jpg&h=9b99e076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細妹IG內連落水濕身相都有，不過江嘉敏就留言取笑阿妹似彊屍。"},{"pid":"397fa3203b21797d507d419adcae051f44e8a8ac","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"去年初江嘉敏曾自爆家中有妹，當時她表示一個14、15歲，一個17、18歲，江嘉敏一直以來都保護兩個妹唔畀真人見光，亦從未把合照放上社交網，不過日前26歲生日就放了一張阿妹視覺照上IG限時動態，唔覺意把17歲的細細妹的IG<br />\n帳號曝光。"},{"pid":"30b923506fb385ea74a045f01796b4eac749a7ab","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"據知江嘉敏細細妹今年17歲，在其IG內有不少與江嘉敏的互動，而她每個post江嘉敏都必定會留言與讚好，可見姊妹關係不錯。至於江嘉敏另一位年約20歲的二妹，其IG帳號一直是私人帳號，不過二妹亦經常在細妹IG留言。"},{"pid":"42a662cdac23f60a4a870d3d32f88babb735b5eb","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cheuky1_106933337_284544965985352_111153741252064935_n_11210338405fa52512234ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fcheuky1_106933337_284544965985352_111153741252064935_n_11210338405fa52512234ce.jpg&h=29c0a025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江家有三姊妹，不過二妹唔想出鏡，在細妹的IG內有三人的合照，不過只係睇到下巴冇見樣。"},{"pid":"2ad2bbd0c3d3b4f19c1c8305874791dec55c1ccc","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"家姐江嘉敏出名寸嘴，細妹亦有樣學樣，在其IG內除了有大量自我覺得好靚的自拍照外，三姊妹亦經常在IG內出言鬥靚，細妹雙眼皮深邃少有化妝，文青味濃，有鄰家女孩感覺。其中一個post細妹讚自己靚，江嘉敏亦唔執輸：「係幾靚嘅不過你家姐靚啲。」細妹即不甘示弱反寸江嘉敏：「係靚過你影嗰啲相嘅，我係素顏美女。」寸爆江嘉敏厚妝兼作狀，細妹加油呀！以家姐為目標，他日一定青出於藍！"},{"pid":"6d3c6995355b8500bc5dc98dc272302ffe85c230","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cheuky1_97144401_270189877721256_3674984756404842575_n_11861410975fa5250cf0fb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fcheuky1_97144401_270189877721256_3674984756404842575_n_11861410975fa5250cf0fb1.jpg&h=0a4c83ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江嘉敏細妹外表算清純，17歲仍在中學階段，不過佢亦好寸嘴。"},{"pid":"75b2f03ddc1549aedd2f0319e1a3fe7075271e03","tid":2274751,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:45:38.000Z","msg":"我ok的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4970c0982ddee70321f08f5d4129933eb3d32648","tid":2274751,"uid":140834,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"8338f577aa94bdbe763bb8fc63b66e3b5778797c","tid":2274751,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/cheuky1_106273080_313206323405717_2720353903420328948_n_12009864885fa5251064609.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fcheuky1_106273080_313206323405717_2720353903420328948_n_12009864885fa5251064609.jpg&h=9b99e076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細妹IG內連落水濕身相都有，不過江嘉敏就留言取笑阿妹似彊屍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFTvPLu.jpg\" data-